 RW-SYS 
 A Tool to Read-write System Images!

Please Enter Selection:

1 - RW the system image from storage
2 - RW the system image from system partition by generating the modded image

also you have to reflash the generated images manually

You can also do:

# rw-sys --file /sdcard/ProjectROM-1.img - Automatically assume you want to rw a certain image from storage

# rw-sys --system  -  Automatically tries to grab /system mappers then set to rw

